---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Flight School Planning Tools | Flight School Friend"
  description="Practical planning tools for estimating cost, comparing schools, and tracking training progress. Template previews for now."
>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">Flight School Planning Tools</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4 leading-relaxed">Practical planning tools for estimating cost, comparing schools, and tracking training progress. These tools are template previews for now.</p>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Some tools are coming soon. Start with the Flight School Decision Tool if you are not sure what to use first.</p>
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold rounded-xl text-lg transition shadow-md">Start Here</a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/" class="block bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 hover:border-sky-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
        <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Live</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Flight School Decision Tool</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Get a personalized starting path based on your goal, budget, timeline, schedule, medical readiness, and confidence level.</p>
        <span class="text-sky-600 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Use the Decision Tool &rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/tools/flight-school-cost-calculator/" class="block bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm">
        <span class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Template Preview</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Flight School Cost Calculator</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">Estimate training cost using aircraft rate, instructor rate, expected hours, ground instruction, testing, supplies, and monthly budget.</p>
        <span class="text-slate-700 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Preview calculator &rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/tools/flight-school-research-scorecard/" class="block bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm">
        <span class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Template Preview</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Flight School Research Scorecard</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">Compare schools side-by-side using pricing transparency, aircraft availability, instructor fit, scheduling, safety culture, and goal fit.</p>
        <span class="text-slate-700 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Preview scorecard &rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/tools/private-pilot-progress-tracker/" class="block bg-white border border-slate-200 hover:border-slate-300 rounded-2xl p-8 transition shadow-sm">
        <span class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Template Preview</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Private Pilot Progress Tracker</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">Track milestones from first lesson through solo, cross-country, written test, checkride prep, and private pilot certification.</p>
        <span class="text-slate-700 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">Preview tracker &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Future tool ideas</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
        {['Discovery Flight Prep Checklist','AME Readiness Planner','Part 61 vs Part 141 Decision Matrix','Checkride Prep Planner','Maneuver Overview Library','Flight Training Budget Tracker'].map(t => (
          <div class="bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-300 border border-slate-700">{t}</div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="text-center border-t border-slate-700 pt-8">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Not sure which tool to use?</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 text-sm">Take the Flight School Decision Tool and get a recommended starting path.</p>
        <a href="/flight-school-decision-tool/quiz/" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold rounded-lg transition">Start Here</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
